data.description: Welcome to your dream country retreat! This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath home is nestled on nearly an acre of picturesque land, just on the outskirts of Lafayette. Step inside and discover a spacious living room, kitchen and primary bedroom suite. Enjoy the luxurious primary bathroom featuring a separate tub and shower--your own private oasis. With a large laundry room and an oversized pantry, this home offers ample storage space for all your needs. As you soak in the tranquility of the quiet country setting, unwind on the expansive front porch, perfect for enjoying serene sunsets or sipping your morning coffee. This home beckons you to embrace the charms of country living while still being conveniently located near Lafayette's amenities and attractions.
